    code xl
    | , and 
    code xxl
    | .
  p
    | Where
    em  side
    |  is one of:
  ul
    li
      code top
      |  - for classes that set style for 
      code border-top
    li
      code bottom
      |  - for  classes that set style for 
      code border-bottom
    li
      code start
      |  - for  classes that set style for 
      code border-left
    li
      code end
      |  - for  classes that set style for 
      code border-right
    li
      code x
      |  - for classes that set both 
      code *-left
      |  and 
      code *-right
    li
      code y
      |  - for classes that set both 
      code *-top
      |  and 
      code *-bottom
    li
      | blank - for classes that set the 
      code border
      |  style on all 4 side of the element.

